title: The Football League Show 29.11.2014
description:
The Football League Show 29.11.2014 

Duration: 1 hour 20 min

Manish Bhasin introduces the drama from all three divisions of the Football League.
Mounting a realistic challenge for promotion under Aitor Karanka, Middlesborough this week welcome Blackburn to the Riverside.
Charlton meanwhile entertain Mick McCarthy's Ipswich at the Valley and from League One there is the best of the action from a top of the table clash as Peterborough meet Bristol City.
